      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "4. Code"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "the system state chart defined in system_state_statechart.h"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We can use MACRO Expansion to get the statechart and transition tables."
